{
  "2362300": {
    "name": "Train Sim World® 4",
    "steam_appid": 2362300,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的爱好—你的冒险—你的方式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/17e4a6417012eb36110192ead4bc79cc.poster.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/17e4a6417012eb36110192ead4bc79cc.webm?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/17e4a6417012eb36110192ead4bc79cc.mp4?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受更多的模拟能力。在《模拟火车世界 4》中体验列车飞驰并展现无与伦比的创造力！扩大你的铁路爱好并找寻驾驶各种标志性线路和列车的初心。从训练中心到山口，你的旅程你做主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全轨道模拟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/27203b9165956f0838905ada3247e17a.poster.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/27203b9165956f0838905ada3247e17a.webm?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/27203b9165956f0838905ada3247e17a.mp4?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在踏上现实世界的铁路之前，先在培训中心学习操作各种车辆牵引的基础知识。该中心现在具有 323 型动车组和 8F 型机车以及 66 型动车组，意味着你可以掌握柴油、蒸汽和电力操作。驾驶适合你的列车，根据全新难度等级你可以对其内容复杂性有些初步了解，全新的设置消除了陷阱区域，建立信心，掌握每一台机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥想象进行创造</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/19217f232b1feb2181d50330930892d1.poster.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/19217f232b1feb2181d50330930892d1.webm?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/19217f232b1feb2181d50330930892d1.mp4?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由驾驶选择你想要的列车并将其驾驶到任何你想去的地方—你现在可以完全用你的方式运行列车线路。拍张照片，让美好的回忆留在“照片模式”和“画廊”中—在动作中间暂停并制作完美的镜头，尽在你的掌握中。用升级过的场景编辑器和涂装编辑器，加上它们现在主打的额外的工具和选项，可以微调你的个性化列车体验。通过“创作者俱乐部”与其他玩家分享你的辛勤工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择你的路径</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/9a891f6b7c5dfee3b1e73d48b168023d.poster.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/9a891f6b7c5dfee3b1e73d48b168023d.webm?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/9a891f6b7c5dfee3b1e73d48b168023d.mp4?t=1764602167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是《模拟火车世界》的新手，还是拥有资深“驾龄”的老手，都能按照自己的节奏开启《模拟火车世界 4》的旅程—各种路径和升级选项可帮助你入门。如果在前作《模拟火车世界》的基础上进行升级，你的收藏和档案进度会继承到新作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/e40a92287455c5bcdf975ef6577748aa.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/5dc1309c35f11a185fae04256f88b283.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362300/extras/f44d6728186b313ee1404344c4b60dac.avif?t=1764602167\" width=616 height=346 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特征</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习在细节丰富的线路上驾驶逼真的列车 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在训练中心深入了解列车驾驶知识 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在引人入胜的场景和繁多的时刻表中测试技能 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用涂装编辑器、场景编辑器和照片模式展现你的创造力 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用自由驾驶自选旅程 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验《模拟火车世界 4》所有全新的可用内容 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东部海岸主线：彼得伯勒站—唐卡斯特站，以及伦敦东北铁路英铁 801 型动车组 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >羚羊谷线：洛杉矶站—兰卡斯特站，以及南加州都会铁道（Metrolink）F125 型机车 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >福拉尔贝格州城市快铁：林道站—布卢登茨站，以及奥铁 4024 型动车组 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豪华版：伦敦东北铁路 A3 60103 型机车“飞翔的苏格兰人号” </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豪华版：Railpool 193 型威克创（Vectron）机车（及德累斯顿区域线—里萨站） </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用未来将要推出的新内容和《模拟火车世界》兼容内容扩展你的收藏 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别版：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英国东南高铁线：伦敦圣潘克拉斯国际站—阿什福德国际站和法弗舍姆站</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西莱茵河铁路：美茵茨站—科布伦茨站</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >法国高速铁路地中海线：马赛站—阿维尼翁站</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东北走廊：波士顿站—普罗维登斯站</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的现有收藏仍然有效 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由多乐堂游戏专属的 SimuGraph® 车辆动力学引擎和虚幻引擎4®技术提供支持 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下载大小将根据购买的内容而有所不同 </p></li></ul>",
